```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant GUI as PyQt5 GUI
    participant DS as LocalDataSource
    participant CPU as CPUMonitor
    participant GPU as GPUMonitor
    participant Logger as DataLogger
    participant DB as SQLite DB
    
    GUI->>DS: get_cpu_info()
    DS->>CPU: get_all_info()
    CPU->>CPU: Read /proc/stat, /proc/cpuinfo
    CPU-->>DS: {usage, freq, temp, ...}
    DS-->>GUI: CPU Data
    
    GUI->>DS: get_gpu_info()
    DS->>GPU: get_all_info()
    GPU->>GPU: Query pynvml/rocm-smi/sysfs
    GPU-->>DS: {util, freq, temp, power, ...}
    DS-->>GUI: GPU Data
    
    GUI->>Logger: log_sample(snapshot)
    Logger->>DB: INSERT INTO monitoring_data
    DB-->>Logger: OK
    
    Note over GUI: Update Charts<br/>Display Metrics
```
